	<h1 class="title">非裔模特形象不够正面？H&amp;M最终为社交媒体上的口无遮拦道了歉</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/194153/small/194153.jpg?1454682827" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">徐婧艾 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-11 18:33:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/17412/medium/17412.jpg?1447231332" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


